items.name: Victoria 2 - Pop Demand Mod Wiki
items.title: Victoria 2 - Pop Demand Mod Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Pop Demand Mod Wikia
items.desc: Pop Demand Mod (PDM) is a mod project for Victoria 2, a real-time grand strategy game published by Paradox Interactive and set in the Victorian era. PDM completely reworks the VIC2 economy, and adds hundreds of new events, decisions and game mechanics, all with the goal of making a more historically plausible and fun experience.

items.title: Victoria Justice Wiki
items.headline: Victoria Justice Wiki
items.desc: Welcome to the Victoria Justice Wiki! This site is dedicated to providing information about Victoria Justice, a popular American actress, singer-songwriter, and dancer. She debuted as an actress at the age of 10 and has since appeared in several films and television series such as the popular Nickelodeon series Zoey 101 and Victorious! Enter the wiki now to learn more!

items.name: Victoria Park IB Wiki
items.title: Victoria Park IB Wiki
items.headline: Your source for all things covered in the Grade 11 IB program at VPCI
items.desc: Dedicated to providing a simple resource for catching up on concepts and knowledge students might need. Volunteers copy their notes into a Wiki article complete with easy-to-read formatting and pictures. It covers a broad swath of topics, from Latin to Economics, and will continue to grow as volunteers contribute.

items.title: Victoria Wiki
items.desc: A wiki about the BBC show. It chronicles the early life of Queen Victoria, from her ascension to the throne at the tender age of 18 to her courtship and marriage to Prince Albert.
